title: Ворон та Воробйов
overview: The plot centers on the story of Voron, an experienced detective who has gone through many trials, and Vorobyov, a younger, naive, and romantic hero. The men have completely different characters and methods of work. While investigating a complicated case, they learn about a gangster's safe with 50 million dollars. To get to the money, the rivals are forced to join forces and become a team.
